{"tid":1826143,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"UEFA最佳陣容 排4-2-4成就C朗？","createTime":"2020-01-16T01:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T05:18:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f403bda68a92a1e7172d8274dbc73ae807c546","tid":1826143,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】由球迷投票選出的歐洲足協最佳陣容出爐，利物浦佔去其中5席，有傳UEFA刻意為遷就C朗安排一個並不常見的陣式。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲足協周三公佈球迷投票選出的2019年最佳陣容，結果歐聯冠軍利物浦成為大贏家，有門神阿里遜、前鋒沙迪奧文尼、中堅雲迪克，以及一對鐵閘阿歷山大阿奴和羅拔臣入圍。11人中，有7人為首次入選<br />\n<br />\n英超佔去其中6席成為大贏家，另一位是曼城中場迪布尼。巴塞隆拿的美斯和法基迪莊分別入選，人數與祖雲達斯不相伯仲，入選者是荷蘭中堅迪列治和球王基斯坦奴朗拿度；拜仁慕尼黑中鋒利雲度夫斯基也躋身其中。C朗連續13年入圍，據《每日郵報》披露，如果是常見陣式，他本不能入圍，但經UEFA把陣式轉為並不常見的4-2-4後，C朗方能入圍。<br />\n<br />\n這個最佳陣容由球迷網上票選，合共有50名球員以供選擇。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"9e04188f73839f03a840b4934a536bc1079dc077","tid":1826143,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.uefa.com/MultimediaFiles/Infographics/competitions/General/02/63/78/52/2637852_MEDIUMSQUARE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uefa.com%2FMultimediaFiles%2FInfographics%2Fcompetitions%2FGeneral%2F02%2F63%2F78%2F52%2F2637852_MEDIUMSQUARE.jpg&h=d3b44b25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80d46a6c63ff53afa9b2e94ba08c3fd9654ca29b","tid":1826143,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/01/15/13/23432468-7890329-image-m-27_1579095442245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F01%2F15%2F13%2F23432468-7890329-image-m-27_1579095442245.jpg&h=6efba3e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2082e90381eef9e2016187e3a341716e81e58435","tid":1826143,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:48:19.000Z","msg":"冇沙拉赫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8763a35